{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>也许应用中最常用到的组件就是Link，可见其重要性。其实Link组件几乎与<a>标签完全一样，除了一点：Link组件可以感知到被激活的路由。我们称当前在界面上显示的路由为被激活的路由。</p>\n<p>紧接上一小节，刚打开网页我们看到的是渲染后的App组件。如果想从App页面导航到Boys页面和Girls页面，就需要在App组件中创建一些导航。代码如下：</p>\n<p>// modules/App.js中\nimport React from 'react'\nimport { Link } from 'react-router'</p>\n<p>export default React.createClass({\nrender() {\nreturn (\n<div>\n<h1>明星特区</h1>\n<ul role=\"nav\">\n<li><Link to=\"/boys\">男神</Link></li>\n<li><Link to=\"/girls\">女神</Link></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n)\n}\n})\n现在再去打包运行（方法见上一节，以后不再重复说了哈），点击访问测试，你会惊奇的发现，点链接、回退、前进，都正常工作了。这就是Link组件的用法。</p>","frontmatter":{"date":"October 21, 2018","title":"Post Number Seven","tags":["gatsby","tutorial","other"],"categores":null,"cover":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1.5025484199796126,"src":"/static/ef64ba6bb722b02d93e341af50253a73/f420b/speed.jpg","srcSet":"/static/ef64ba6bb722b02d93e341af50253a73/9d775/speed.jpg 480w,\n/static/ef64ba6bb722b02d93e341af50253a73/8ba9e/speed.jpg 960w,\n/static/ef64ba6bb722b02d93e341af50253a73/f420b/speed.jpg 1474w","srcWebp":"/static/ef64ba6bb722b02d93e341af50253a73/1ddf2/speed.webp","srcSetWebp":"/static/ef64ba6bb722b02d93e341af50253a73/70ab6/speed.webp 480w,\n/static/ef64ba6bb722b02d93e341af50253a73/5a631/speed.webp 960w,\n/static/ef64ba6bb722b02d93e341af50253a73/1ddf2/speed.webp 1474w","sizes":"(max-width: 1474px) 100vw, 1474px"},"resize":{"src":"/static/ef64ba6bb722b02d93e341af50253a73/d260a/speed.jpg"}}}}}},"pageContext":{"pathSlug":"/post-seven","prev":{"id":"28a8ec39-aa7a-55e7-9327-4a1128f36855","excerpt":"也许应用中最常用到的组件就是Link，可见其重要性。其实Link组件几乎与 标签完全一样，除了一点：Link组件可以感知到被激活的路由。我们称当前在界面上显示的路由为被激活的路由。 紧接上一小节，刚打开网页我们看到的是渲染后的App组件。如果想从App页面导航到Boys页面和Girls页面，就需要在App组件中创建一些导航。代码如下： // modules/App.js中\nimport React from 'react'\nimport { Link } from 'react-router…","frontmatter":{"date":"October 21, 2018","path":"/post-seven","title":"Post Number Seven","tags":["gatsby","tutorial","other"],"categores":null}},"